GeneralComments: This charger is powered by 100% self-made solar energy. Due to this charging is only possible if it’s a sunny day. Please contact me a few minutes before arriving to check whether charging is available: +4915738161241  Charging speed may vary due to weather changes. It dynamically charges from 1 Phase 6A up to 3 Phase 8A.  If it gets cloudy, charging may stop and continue when there’s enough energy available.
